      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition, offering reliable transportation for a driver who values function over form. The engine starts consistently and the transmission shifts through all gears, though you may notice some typical age-related vibrations and minor fluid seeps. Externally, the paint shows fading and several noticeable scratches and door dings, while the interior has visible wear on the upholstery and a few cracked trim pieces. It has been a dependable daily driver, but it will likely require some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in top shape.",
