    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! If you're looking for a reliable ride that's ready for its next adventure, you've found it! This car has been so good to me and is still in wonderful shape, running smooth and looking great. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019re going to love how it handles. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
