    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example is equipped with a traditional 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal torque distribution. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing, maintaining the chassis's torsional rigidity. The suspension remains tight with refreshed control arm bushings and dampers, preserving the communicative steering feel this platform is known for. While the exterior displays minor road-going patina, the drivetrain remains robust and responsive, making this a quintessential driver\u2019s car for the purist.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Maintenance records available. Clean title. Interior is well-kept. Minor cosmetic wear on exterior. Engine and transmission perform reliably.",
