    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I'm parting with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-loved and carefully maintained, so you know it\u2019s got plenty of adventures left in it! It's super clean, runs smoothly, and is perfect for everything from the daily commute to weekend road trips. I've honestly loved owning this car, and I'm sure you will too. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
