      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a meticulously maintained driver\u2019s specimen featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional corner-exit traction. The chassis remains composed with refreshed suspension bushings and a reinforced rear subframe, mitigating common platform fatigue. While the exterior displays minor, age-consistent patina, the mechanical vitals are robust, including a recently serviced VANOS system and valve adjustment. It rides on staggered alloy wheels wrapped in high-performance rubber, offering the precise turn-in and feedback expected of a true M-division icon.",
